That and arrogance are probably the roots of douchy so also make sure you don't come off as arrogant. I know you're not an arrogant guy but a lot of people think you come off as one. Try to be original, people, now especially I think, really appreciate originality. Even if you're not really witty or anything, individual personality is pretty key. Also try to find a balance between talking a lot and being silent. I would say find a balance in everything. When you're not around you're very good friends, be conscious of yourself, but not overly conscious, self conscious. Again a balance.
